sk.stuba.fiit.perconik.core.adapters

Class PerspectiveAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • sk.stuba.fiit.perconik.core.AbstractRegistrable
      • sk.stuba.fiit.perconik.core.Adapter
        • sk.stuba.fiit.perconik.core.adapters.PerspectiveAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.eclipse.ui.IPerspectiveListener, org.eclipse.ui.IPerspectiveListener2, org.eclipse.ui.IPerspectiveListener3, org.eclipse.ui.IPerspectiveListener4, Listener, PerspectiveListener, Registrable

    public class PerspectiveAdapter
extends Adapter
implements PerspectiveListener
    An abstract adapter class for a PerspectiveListener. The methods in this class are empty. This class exists as convenience for creating listener objects.

    Extend this class to create a PerspectiveListener and override the methods for the events of interest.

    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Pavol Zbell
    See Also:
    Adapter, PerspectiveListener
